<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>caption</tag> is an extended description of a
<tag>mediaobject</tag> or <tag>figure</tag> or other formal or informal
element. Unlike a <tag>textobject</tag>, which is an
alternative to the other elements in the <tag>mediaobject</tag>, the
<tag>caption</tag> augments the object.
</para>

